{"tid":614285,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"文尼呼冤：我冇插水！","createTime":"2018-04-02T11:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T11:53:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec4072f1acb08908060f0a43b612769c96172ee","tid":614285,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/3/423/20924820423/20932259907_600x406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F3%2F423%2F20924820423%2F20932259907_600x406.jpg&h=8ff1e631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=43fe54d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】在上周六英超，利物浦翼鋒沙迪奧文尼因為插水被罰黃牌，他事後大表冤枉。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦上仗作客水晶宮，憑沙迪奧文尼（Sadio Mane）及穆罕默德沙拿建功，以2:1反勝全取3分。文尼曾在禁區被對方中場麥亞瑟攔跌，球證未有判罰12碼之餘，更以插水的罪名向文尼出示黃牌。<br />\n<br />\n文尼表示：「老實說，我當時真的以為球證會給予12碼。他決定不判罰極刑，不過我沒有在意，因為這是比賽的一部份。當然，我是可以更好運的。我只會盡力比賽，最終我也能取得入球。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然沙拿絕殺得手，但文尼才是焦點人物，他在下半場跟對手過招後倒地，突然用手把皮球拿起，球證吹罰他手球，卻沒有再出示黃牌。幸運地逃過被逐的文尼說：「球證沒有吹罰對方攔截我，我真的很驚訝。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"4207e354adb12159adcd2a4247fa7a97243cf7cc","tid":614285,"uid":16376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"d力架無腦"},{"pid":"a7d6e167b7e3b84768ad6eb72ae7e1adefddcdc2","tid":614285,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4207e354adb12159adcd2a4247fa7a97243cf7cc","tid":614285,"uid":16376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"d力架無腦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"埃及文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2447e87e703c219975eff4e1624dcb7b767458","tid":614285,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"狗只會跳水<br />\n不會插水"},{"pid":"b